headline: Energy Stocks Break Their Slump. Which Charts Are Most Bullish?
summary: Energy has lagged over the past year, with the  ranking ninth of 11 major sectors.  Over the past three months, energy has moved up to become the third-best performer.  This relative strength is likely to remain a theme in 2026.
